#. <a class="sc" id="sc139"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:3.2.8"
msgid ""
"‘Nevantavā nānantavā attā hoti arogo paraṃ maraṇā asaññī’ti naṃ paññapenti. "
"(8: 42)"
