#. <a class="sc" id="sc151"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:3.9.1"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā ucchedavādā sato sattassa ucchedaṃ "
"vināsaṃ vibhavaṃ paññapenti sattahi vatthūhi."
