msgctxt "dn1:3.17.1"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho te, bhikkhave, samaṇabrāhmaṇā ucchedavādā sato sattassa ucchedaṃ "
"vināsaṃ vibhavaṃ paññapenti sattahi vatthūhi."
