"aññatra phassā paṭisaṃvedissantīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.63"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc203"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:3.63.1"
msgid ""
"Tatra, bhikkhave, ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā pubbantakappikā pubbantānudiṭṭhino "
"pubbantaṃ ārabbha anekavihitāni adhimuttipadāni abhivadanti aṭṭhārasahi "
"vatthūhi, te vata aññatra phassā paṭisaṃvedissantīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.64"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.44"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc204"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:3.64.1"
msgid ""
"Tatra, bhikkhave, ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā uddhamāghātanikā saññīvādā "
"uddhamāghātanaṃ saññiṃ attānaṃ paññapenti soḷasahi vatthūhi, te vata aññatra "
"phassā paṭisaṃvedissantīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.65"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc205"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:3.65.1"
msgid ""
"Tatra, bhikkhave, ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā uddhamāghātanikā asaññīvādā, "
"uddhamāghātanaṃ asaññiṃ attānaṃ paññapenti aṭṭhahi vatthūhi, te vata aññatra "
"phassā paṭisaṃvedissantīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.66"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc206"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:3.66.1"
msgid ""
"Tatra, bhikkhave, ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā uddhamāghātanikā nevasaññīnāsaññīvādā "
"uddhamāghātanaṃ nevasaññīnāsaññiṃ attānaṃ paññapenti aṭṭhahi vatthūhi, te "
"vata aññatra phassā paṭisaṃvedissantīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.67"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc207"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:3.67.1"
msgid ""
"Tatra, bhikkhave, ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā ucchedavādā sato sattassa ucchedaṃ "
"vināsaṃ vibhavaṃ paññapenti sattahi vatthūhi, te vata aññatra phassā "
"paṭisaṃvedissantīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.68"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc208"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:3.68.1"
msgid ""
"Tatra, bhikkhave, ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā diṭṭhadhammanibbānavādā sato sattassa "
"paramadiṭṭhadhammanibbānaṃ paññapenti pañcahi vatthūhi, te vata aññatra "
"phassā paṭisaṃvedissantīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.69"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc209"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:3.69.1"
msgid ""
"Tatra, bhikkhave, ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā aparantakappikā aparantānudiṭṭhino "
"aparantaṃ ārabbha anekavihitāni adhimuttipadāni abhivadanti catucattārīsāya "
"vatthūhi, te vata aññatra phassā paṭisaṃvedissantīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.70"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc210"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:3.70.1"
msgid ""
"Tatra, bhikkhave, ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā pubbantakappikā ca aparantakappikā ca "
"pubbantāparantakappikā ca pubbantāparantānudiṭṭhino pubbantāparantaṃ ārabbha "
"anekavihitāni adhimuttipadāni abhivadanti dvāsaṭṭhiyā vatthūhi, te vata "
"aññatra phassā paṭisaṃvedissantīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "dn1:3.70.2"
msgid "4.4. Diṭṭhigatikādhiṭṭhānavaṭṭakathā"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.71"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.45"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc211"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:3.71.1"
msgid ""
"Tatra, bhikkhave, ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā sassatavādā sassataṃ attānañca "
"lokañca paññapenti catūhi vatthūhi, yepi te samaṇabrāhmaṇā ekaccasassatikā "
"ekaccaasassatikā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.71.2"
msgid "yepi te samaṇabrāhmaṇā antānantikā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.71.3"
msgid "yepi te samaṇabrāhmaṇā amarāvikkhepikā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.71.4"
msgid "yepi te samaṇabrāhmaṇā adhiccasamuppannikā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.71.5"
msgid "yepi te samaṇabrāhmaṇā pubbantakappikā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.71.6"
msgid "yepi te samaṇabrāhmaṇā uddhamāghātanikā saññīvādā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.71.7"
msgid "yepi te samaṇabrāhmaṇā uddhamāghātanikā asaññīvādā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.71.8"
msgid "yepi te samaṇabrāhmaṇā uddhamāghātanikā nevasaññīnāsaññīvādā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.71.9"
msgid "yepi te samaṇabrāhmaṇā ucchedavādā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.71.10"
msgid "yepi te samaṇabrāhmaṇā diṭṭhadhammanibbānavādā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.71.11"
msgid "yepi te samaṇabrāhmaṇā aparantakappikā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.71.12"
msgid ""
"yepi te samaṇabrāhmaṇā pubbantakappikā ca aparantakappikā ca "
"pubbantāparantakappikā ca pubbantāparantānudiṭṭhino pubbantāparantaṃ ārabbha "
"anekavihitāni adhimuttipadāni abhivadanti dvāsaṭṭhiyā vatthūhi, sabbe te "
"chahi phassāyatanehi phussa phussa paṭisaṃvedenti tesaṃ vedanāpaccayā taṇhā, "
"taṇhāpaccayā upādānaṃ, upādānapaccayā bhavo, bhavapaccayā jāti, jātipaccayā "
"jarāmaraṇaṃ sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsā sambhavanti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn1:3.71.13"
msgid "5. Vivaṭṭakathādi"
msgstr ""

#. </h2><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc212"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:3.71.14"
msgid ""
"Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu channaṃ phassāyatanānaṃ samudayañca "
"atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ayaṃ "
"imehi sabbeheva uttaritaraṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.72"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc213"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:3.72.1"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā pubbantakappikā vā "
"aparantakappikā vā pubbantāparantakappikā vā pubbantāparantānudiṭṭhino "
"pubbantāparantaṃ ārabbha anekavihitāni adhimuttipadāni abhivadanti, sabbe te "
"imeheva dvāsaṭṭhiyā vatthūhi antojālīkatā, ettha sitāva ummujjamānā "
"ummujjanti, ettha pariyāpannā antojālīkatāva ummujjamānā ummujjanti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.46"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc214"></a>
#. VAR: udakadahaṃ → udakarahadaṃ (s1-3)
msgctxt "dn1:3.72.2"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, dakkho kevaṭṭo vā kevaṭṭantevāsī vā sukhumacchikena "
"jālena parittaṃ udakadahaṃ otthareyya. Tassa evamassa: ‘ye kho keci imasmiṃ "
"udakadahe oḷārikā pāṇā, sabbe te antojālīkatā. Ettha sitāva ummujjamānā "
"ummujjanti; ettha pariyāpannā antojālīkatāva ummujjamānā ummujjantī’ti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.72.3"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, ye hi keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā pubbantakappikā vā "
"aparantakappikā vā pubbantāparantakappikā vā pubbantāparantānudiṭṭhino "
"pubbantāparantaṃ ārabbha anekavihitāni adhimuttipadāni abhivadanti, sabbe te "
"imeheva dvāsaṭṭhiyā vatthūhi antojālīkatā ettha sitāva ummujjamānā "
"ummujjanti, ettha pariyāpannā antojālīkatāva ummujjamānā ummujjanti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.73"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc215"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:3.73.1"
msgid "Ucchinnabhavanettiko, bhikkhave, tathāgatassa kāyo tiṭṭhati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.73.2"
msgid "Yāvassa kāyo ṭhassati, tāva naṃ dakkhanti devamanussā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.73.3"
msgid "Kāyassa bhedā uddhaṃ jīvitapariyādānā na naṃ dakkhanti devamanussā."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc216"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:3.73.4"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ambapiṇḍiyā vaṇṭacchinnāya yāni kānici ambāni "
"vaṇṭapaṭibandhāni, sabbāni tāni tadanvayāni bhavanti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.73.5"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, ucchinnabhavanettiko tathāgatassa kāyo tiṭṭhati, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.73.6"
msgid "yāvassa kāyo ṭhassati, tāva naṃ dakkhanti devamanussā, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.73.7"
msgid "kāyassa bhedā uddhaṃ jīvitapariyādānā na naṃ dakkhanti devamanussā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.74"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc217"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:3.74.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.74.2"
msgid ""
"“acchariyaṃ, bhante, abbhutaṃ, bhante, ko nāmo ayaṃ, bhante, "
"dhammapariyāyo”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.74.3"
msgid ""
"“Tasmātiha tvaṃ, ānanda, imaṃ dhammapariyāyaṃ atthajālantipi naṃ dhārehi, "
"dhammajālantipi naṃ dhārehi, brahmajālantipi naṃ dhārehi, diṭṭhijālantipi "
"naṃ dhārehi, anuttaro saṅgāmavijayotipi naṃ dhārehī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc218"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:3.74.4"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn1:3.74.5"
msgid "Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: dasasahassī → sahassī (pts1)
msgctxt "dn1:3.74.6"
msgid ""
"Imasmiñca pana veyyākaraṇasmiṃ bhaññamāne dasasahassī lokadhātu akampitthāti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "dn1:3.74.7"
msgid "Brahmajālasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
